  Entirely fabricated test data: no real patient, no PHI.

  Two vitals series chosen so observation_table and
  observation_relationship have exact, hand-checkable answers:
    - body weight (29463-7) on Jan 15/16/17/18: 380 / 400 / 420 / 440
